text: Redundant features: Sales tax paid is perfectly correlated by item. However, across items the rate of sales tax paid varies. That is not all countries charges the same rate of sale tax for RAW FOOD and Restaurant food.  Temperature expressed in degrees Kelvin and  degrees Celsius qualify. So would temperature expressed in degrees Fahrenheit alongside either of these as there is a known mathematical relationship. Distance expressed in Kilometers and Miles also qualifies as there is a known mathematical relationship.  We could extend that to light years too, again because of the known mathematical relationship.
